  "body": "<h1><br><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/st35XgD.png\"></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #f1c40f;\">If enough love is given to this mod, an eventual update adding the more golems is planned.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eZqO2q0.png\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ced4d9;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/moregolems\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1452714?logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=eb622b&amp;labelColor=black&amp;color=eb622b\" alt=\"CurseForge Downloads\" width=\"161\" height=\"27\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/moregolems\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/moregolems?logo=modrinth&amp;labelColor=black&amp;color=1bd96a\" alt=\"CurseForge Downloads\" width=\"175\" height=\"30\"></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codderg.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Wiki-Read-2ea44f?logo=wikipedia&amp;logoColor=white&amp;style=flat&amp;labelColor=111\" alt=\"Wiki\" width=\"131\" height=\"30\"></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ced4d9;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Andresv2017\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub-Andresv2017-6F42C1?logo=github&amp;logoColor=white&amp;style=flat&amp;labelColor=111\" alt=\"GitHub\" width=\"228\" height=\"31\"></a>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #ced4d9;\"><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/BrvQ4AWGYu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/dynamic/json?url=https://discord.com/api/guilds/1385048182152626296/widget.json&amp;query=presence_count&amp;style=flat&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Discord&amp;color=5865F2&amp;labelColor=111\" alt=\"